&lt;p&gt;I think the main reason my blogging has almost become nil is that I&amp;#8217;m not sure what I want to use this blog for.  I&amp;#8217;m on Twitter.  I run the CVREG. I just don&amp;#8217;t know what to do this blog.  I had ideas.  But I don&amp;#8217;t have the enthusiasm and energy right now - I&amp;#8217;ve been focusing those on the projects I&amp;#8217;m either running or helping with; maybe I&amp;#8217;ll talk about my projects (at a high-level since I&amp;#8217;m under NDA for some).&lt;/p&gt;

